column5: He heard voices in the forest, he heard voices in his head. Magnetized, he couldn't help himself, he followed what he heard and went deep into the forest. He found a small shrine.    He didn't feel well. He had the urge to urinate, but couldn't, his penis had turned to stone.   He wanted to free himself from the demons but couldn't, his knife had turned to stone.   He needed to call for help, but couldn't, his phone had turned to stone.    He couldn't find his way home for his eyes had turned to stone.    He dead
